OL,3,CWhat is a 'recall petition' and why
OL,4,Chas it been triggered?
OL,6,FA 'recall petition' has been triggered
OL,7,Fin the House of Commons .
OL,9,F'Recall petitions' are used to trigger
OL,10,Fan election to remove an MP from their
OL,11,Frole, away from scheduled elections.
OL,13,FIn the UK, a recall can only be
OL,14,Fstarted under specific circumstances:
OL,16,FIn the case of Scott Benton, a recall
OL,17,Fpetition was launched after he was
OL,18,Fsuspended from the Commons for 35
OL,19,Fdays, after offering to lobby
OL,20,Fministers over gambling.
